item.title: Midjourney & Better Call Saul
item.description: Recently, my favorite tv show, Better Call Saul, has ended, and it ended spectacularly Midjourney is a public-facing text-to-image generator that I found often more fun and artistic than DALL-E. To pay tribute to this amazing show, here are some Midjourney generations regarding BCS. It’s really amazing how the model captures the show’s visual style, and might have predicted Saul’s fate in prison! The Generations Saul in prison, black and white “Saul Gone” poster, black and white “Saul Gone” poster black and white 2: The prison bars and the head figure in “A” largely exceeded my expectations for AI generated art.
